te":"2026-04-06 09:54:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_03111432.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"AWS Machine Learning Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":11,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_fbc2be89","title":"使用 Amazon Bedrock 和 Amazon OpenSearch 构建混合 RAG 解决方案的智能搜索 | Amazon Web Services","link":"https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/machine-learning/building-intelligent-search-with-amazon-bedrock-and-amazon-opensearch-for-hybrid-rag-solutions/","date":"2026-04-06 09:49:32","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_fbc2be89.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"AWS Machine Learning Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":13,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_291aabf8","title":"从孤立警报到情境智能：基于生成式 AI 的智能体海事异常分析 | Amazon Web Services","link":"https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/machine-learning/from-isolated-alerts-to-contextual-intelligence-agentic-maritime-anomaly-analysis-with-generative-ai/","date":"2026-04-06 09:48:54","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_291aabf8.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"AWS Machine Learning Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":7,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_e257bb02","title":"一城一段提示词，300+ 座城市美食图鉴","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&mid=2247515114&idx=1&sn=008b54856318448c2c12f0e60f2c4f17","date":"2026-04-06 06:56:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_e257bb02.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"赛博禅心","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":11,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_6ac528ea","title":"使用授权码流程将 MCP 服务器连接到 Amazon Bedrock AgentCore Gateway | Amazon Web Services","link":"https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/machine-learning/connecting-mcp-servers-to-amazon-bedrock-agentcore-gateway-using-authorization-code-flow/","date":"2026-04-06 06:41:46","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_6ac528ea.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"AWS Mac