re":88},{"id":"RAW_a612e00d","title":"没有 KPI，也能领先 OpenAI？从“内部观察者”视角看顶级 AI 实验室如何运作","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NDA4NjU2MA==&mid=2247660458&idx=1&sn=2fc9e28542b7ec2641ef1c2a0f6d1d77","date":"2026-04-06 02:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_a612e00d.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"AI前线","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":41,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_3edcecc6","title":"智能时代的产业政策","link":"https://openai.com/index/industrial-policy-for-the-intelligence-age","date":"2026-04-06 02:30:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_3edcecc6.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"OpenAI Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":1,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_639f093f","title":"发布：datasette-ports 0.1","link":"https://simonwillison.net/2026/Apr/6/datasette-ports/#atom-everything","date":"2026-04-06 00:23:55","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_639f093f.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Simon Willison's Weblog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":1,"score":78},{"id":"RAW_d026ea28","title":"布隆过滤器：理论、工程权衡与 Go 语言实现","link":"https://www.infoq.com/articles/bloom-filters-practice-go-recommender/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-04-07 09:00:00","oneSentenceSummary":"一份关于在 Go 中实现和调优布隆过滤器的综合指南，旨在通过减少昂贵的负向查询来优化高吞吐量推荐系统。","summary":"本文探讨了布隆过滤器在处理每秒 18，000 次请求的推荐流水线中的实际应用。它解决了在 97%-98% 的检查结果为负向的工作负载中进行精确查询的低效问题。通过引入布隆过滤器作为内存中的成员资格网关，团队将 p95 延迟降低了 31%，后端读取流量减少了 70%。文章提供了逐步的 Go 实现方案，解释了参数选择（m 和 k）背后的数学原理，并提供了关于哈希函数选择、生命周期管理和运维监控的工程最佳实践。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_d026ea28.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":16,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_adf08c44","title":"【早说】不用 IDE，只用计划文件和语音：所知道的 Claude Code 全部技巧","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&mid=2651278878&idx=1&sn=6c046dd000e27096fef7277b4f7ab421","date":"2026-04-07 01:01:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文介绍了 Matt Van Horn 基于 Claude Code 构建的全新 AI 驱动工作流，核心在于弃用传统 IDE，通过语音输入、计划文件（plan.md）和多会话并行实现高效开发与决策。","summary":"文章详细阐述了一套颠覆传统的 AI 辅助开发模式。作者主张将 80% 的精力投入到规划阶段，利用 Claude Code 的 `/ce:plan` 命令生成详尽的 `plan.md` 文件，再由 AI 代理执行。该工作流集成了语音转文字工具（如 Monologue）、Ghostty 多窗口并行会话、以及针对 Claude Code 的权限跳过和声音提醒配置。此外，作者还分享了如何结合 `/last30days` 进行实时技术调研，利用 Mac Mini 实现远程控制，并将此工作流扩展至商业战略、会议纪要整理乃至生活旅行规划中，展示了从“手写代码”向“口述规划”的范式转移。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_adf08c44.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"前端早读课","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":23,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_95914716","title":"GitHub Copilot CLI 结合不同模型系列提供“第二意见”","link":"https://github.blog/ai-and-ml/github-copilot/github-copilot-cli-combines-model-families-for-a-second-opinion/","date":"2026-04-06 21:53:51","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_95914716.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"The GitHub Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":4,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_dc8e4f80","title":"如何将 JavaScript 中的 API 调用从“玩具级”提升至生产就绪的网络通信","link":"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/how-to-go-from-toy-api-calls-to-production-ready-networking-in-javascript/","date":"2026-04-06 21:45:49","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_dc8e4f80.json","topicTag":"frontend-fullstack","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"freeCodeCamp.org","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":13,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_ef0d0680","title":"如何使用 OpenClaw 构建并保护个人 AI 智能体","link":"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/how-to-build-and-secure-a-personal-ai-agent-with-openclaw/","date":"2026-04-06 21:44:44","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_ef0d0680.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"freeCodeCamp.org","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":17,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_a648dda5","title":"如何在 Kubernetes 中对用户进行身份验证：x509 证书、OIDC 和云身份","link":"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/